gree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪整H 車多m</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師傅幾好，d野跟得唔錯，同埋師傅算後生（30幾歲我估）、我覺得後生師傅易溝通D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1be52e3a3b8e50aaa4b594fb8c1d44d7c802269","tid":236754,"uid":99394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T10:18:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無將軍澳巴絲覺得將軍澳無車房都幾不便<br />\n利申：去開個間係屯門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屯門邊間？同求</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMotor Plus <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪整H 車多m</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師傅幾好，d野跟得唔錯，同埋師傅算後生（30幾歲我估）、我覺得後生師傅易溝通D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n等我試下先 有機會"},{"pid":"474b86199fa65f68403050bb32a8cbfa9e281e06","tid":236754,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"九龍灣應該搵到間啱你嘅"},{"pid":"964c55f90da82ef9aca864c5e7cc2357bf3d903d","tid":236754,"uid":50899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T11:42:26.000Z","msg":"師兄，九龍灣有無咩車房算平？"},{"pid":"a7fbf154505d09ba37700411fb6639ed69160ecd","tid":236754,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T11:44:38.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣"},{"pid":"25b989d64c7ddc19c96756a4cfea22b0c2b85cbf","tid":236754,"uid":16094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:10:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>九龍灣應該搵到間啱你嘅</blockquote><br />\n巴打有無邊間介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f23cf611eb6242d7797a74296c3b271d46c1b7","tid":236754,"uid":16094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:11:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>土瓜灣</blockquote><br />\n土瓜灣有間去開做音響、鏡頭幾好"},{"pid":"f25688dc3c4240e714d83ce5654bbee1c72c081d","tid":236754,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,